root.name: Awakenings Eindhoven 2016
root.description: Awakenings' Eindhoven takeovers have become one of the highlights of the city's music calendar. As any techno fan will tell you, Awakenings events have become their pilgrimage, where they go for a guarantee of the biggest and best DJs on the scene, and the chance to see those hot tips before anyone else. 2016's edition lives up to that reputation, laying on a bill that boasts Chris Liebing, Joris Voorn and tINI, who will each spin tracks under huge light shows - another given when it comes to Awakenings - which have even led to Richie Hawtin describing the nights as "world class".
